	Warning fixes and support to pass the http headers along with
	cache data items

	* Cache.subproj/NSURICacheData.h, Cache.subproj/NSURICacheData.m:
	(+[NSURICacheData
	dataWithURL:status:error:headers:data:size:notificationString:userData:],
